OL,3,CMan suffers serious injuries after
OL,4,Cfight breaks out in Birmingham
OL,6,FThree people are in custody today
OL,7,Fafter a man was seriously injured in
OL,8,FBirmingham.
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police were called to
OL,11,FCotterills Lane shortly after 2am on
OL,12,FSunday, 7 June, after reports of
OL,13,Fpeople 'fighting in the street'.
OL,15,FA man was taken to hospital with
OL,16,Fserious injuries to his head and body
OL,17,Fand three people were arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of attempted murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
