OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1780927877
OL,3,CMan suffers serious injuries after
OL,4,Cfight breaks out in Birmingham
OL,6,FHis injuries are not thought to be
OL,7,Flife-threatening. All three people
OL,8,Farrested remain in custody while
OL,9,Fpolice investigation continues.
OL,11,FOfficers are remaining at the scene
OL,12,Fthroughout the day today to carry out
OL,13,Fenquiries and speak to witnesses.
OL,15,FThey are keen to speak to anyone who
OL,16,Fwas in the area and who may have seen
OL,17,Fwhat happened or might have photos or
OL,18,Fvideos showing the incident.
OL,20,FAnyone with information should call
OL,21,Fcall 101, quoting log 377 of 7 June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
